Package: atusyverse
Title: Easily Install and Load Select Packages
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("YASUMOTO Atsushi", , email = "atusy.7+atusyverse@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: The 'atusyverse' is selection of packages designed to be loaded
    in concert. The purpose of this package is to make it easy to install and 
    subsequently load those packages.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1)
